               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18371127-name-923" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18371127-name-923" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18371127-name-923" type="surname" value="NASH"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18371127-name-923" type="given" value="JOSEPH"></interp>JOSEPH NASH</persName>
                  </hi>. I live in Claremont-square. On the afternoon of the 20th of November I was in St. James's Park—my attention was called by a constable behind me saying that I had lost my handkerchief—the constable had got it—I believe this is it—I have no mark on it—I know it by the pattern.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
