                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable L</hi> 31.) I was in the Park, and saw the prisoner force his way between two gentlemen, and go to the prosecutor, take this handkerchief from him, and put it down on his right side—my brother officer seized him, and told the gentleman his pocket had been picked.</p>
               <p>
